        <div class="mt-5 container is-flex is-flex-direction-column is-align-items-flex-start gap20px">

            <div class="box">
                <div class="is-size-5 mb-3">Game parameters:</div>
                <div style="min-height:50px;">
                    <label class="radio">
                        <input type="radio" id="chbS" name="parameters" onchange="setGameParameters([5,5,5]);">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-s mr-3"></i>5Wx5Hx5M
                    </label>
                </div>
                <div style="min-height:50px;">
                    <label class="radio">
                        <input type="radio" id="chbM" name="parameters" checked onchange="setGameParameters([10,10,20]);">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-m mr-3"></i>10Wx10Hx20M
                    </label>
                </div>
                <div style="min-height:50px;">
                    <label class="radio">
                        <input type="radio" id="chbXL" name="parameters" onchange="setGameParameters([20,20,100]);">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-l mr-3"></i>20Wx20Hx100M
                    </label>
                </div>
                <div style="min-height:50px;">
                    <div class="container is-flex is-flex-direction-row is-align-items-center gap20px">
                        <label class="radio">
                            <input type="radio" id="chbCustom" name="parameters">
                            Custom
                        </label>

                        <div class="field">
                            <p class="control has-icons-left has-icons-right">
                                <input class="input ma-w-120" type="number" id="playingFieldWidthInput" placeholder="Width" min="5" max="20" onchange="setGameParamsToCustom();">
                                <span class="icon is-small is-left">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrows-left-right"></i>
                                </span>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="field">
                            <p class="control has-icons-left has-icons-right">
                                <input class="input ma-w-120" type="number" id="playingFieldHeightInput" placeholder="Height" min="5" max="20">
                                <span class="icon is-small is-left">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrows-up-down"></i>
                                </span>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="field">
                            <p class="control has-icons-left has-icons-right">
                                <input class="input ma-w-120" type="number" id="minesAmountInput" placeholder="Mines">
                                <span class="icon is-small is-left">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-asterisk"></i>
                                </span>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="field"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-3 mr-3" style="min-height:50px;">
                    <label class="checkbox" id="timedModeSwitch">
                        <input type="checkbox" id="chbTimedMode">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-stopwatch mr-3 ml-3 is-size-3"></i>Timed Mode
                    </label>
                </div>
                <div style="min-height:50px;">
                    <button class="button" style="min-width:120px;" onclick="continueGame()" id="continueGameButton"><i class="fa-solid fa-play mr-3"></i>Resume</button>
                    <button class="button" style="min-width:120px;" onclick="pauseGame()" id="pauseGameButton"><i class="fa-solid fa-pause mr-3"></i>Pause</button>
                    <button class="button" onclick="resetGame()"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-rotate-right mr-3"></i>Start new game</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-3">
            <article class="message is-info">
                <div class="message-header">
                    Instructions
                    <button class="delete"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="message-body">
                    <p>The objective of the game is to find all the hidden mines in the field. </p>
                    <p>Start by clicking on any cell marked with a question mark. If you're unlucky, you'll hit a mine and you will have to start over</p>
                    <p>If you're lucky, you will open a cell (or a set of cells) that show you how many mines are around them. Then, using logic, you can right-click cells to mark them as mines.</p>
                    <p><img src="~/static/minesGameResources/minesGame-1.gif" /></p>
                    <p>Once you have the correct amount of mines identified around a cell, you can double-click it to reveal the other hidden cells. </p>
                    <p><img src="~/static/minesGameResources/minesGame-2.gif" /></p>
                    <p>The game ends when you either identify all mines correctly:</p>
                    <p><img src="~/static/minesGameResources/minesGame-1.gif" /></p>
                    <p>Or when you make a mistake:</p>
                    <p><img src="~/static/minesGameResources/minesGame-1.gif" /></p>
                    <p>Getting a small hint adds 10 seconds to the overall time. Getting a large hint opens up a bigger chunk of the field but adds 30 seconds to your overall time</p>
                    <p>Timed mode gives you a limited amount of time to solve the field. If time ran out before you found all mines -- boom! You lost. </p>
                    <p>You can pause the game, the timer will stop. You can resume the game later.</p>
                    @*<p><img src="~/static/minesGameResources/minesGame-1.gif" /></p>*@
                    @*<p>images here</p>*@
                    @*<p>Informational panel shows your elapsed/remaining time, and shows how many mines are left to find.</p>*@
                    @*<p>images here</p>*@
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 container flex-direction-vertical mi-wi-300 is-hidden" id="scoreboardDiv">
            <div>
                <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-flag-checkered mr-3"></i>Scoreboard:</h2>
                <ol id="results" class="ml-3 mt-2"></ol>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="m-6 container flex-direction-vertical mi-wi-300">
        <div class="mb-2">
            <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-chess-bishop mr-3"></i>Current game:</h2>
        </div>
        <div id="timerArea"><i class="fa-regular fa-clock mr-2"></i><span id="timerHeaderString"></span>: <div id="timerValue" style="min-height:60px;"></div></div>
        <div id="remainingMineCounterArea"><i class="fa-solid fa-asterisk mr-2 mt-3"></i><span id="minesLeft"></span> mine<span id="minesPluralOrSingular"></span> left</div>
    </div>
</div>

